# Guidelines:
# - Use [Conventional commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/#summary)
# - Use imperative voice ("Add feature" not "Added feature")
# - Separate subject from body with blank line
# - Reference tickets and issues in the footer `[ticket]:https://example.com/ticket-123`
# - Format commit messages to fit GitHub pull request fields:
#   - Limit first line to 50 chars `type(scope): description [[ticket-123]]`
#   - Wrap text at 72 chars
#
# Structure:
# 1. What was changed? (already in subject)
# 2. Why was it changed? (root cause/reason)
# 3. How does it address the issue?
# 4. What side effects might this change have?
